name: Weariful Perseverance (1981)
description: This is a portrait of an unidentified woman. The weathered traits of this piece reflect the emotions within the subject. A timeless classic that represents modern struggles. This piece was hand-made in physical medium. The artist is Clyde Higaki, a Silicon Valley native who predates the dot com boom. Raised in the Summer of Love, Clyde offers his work up to the art industry's newest frontier. Limited to 100 editions. Follow @tyhigaki for more.
